CREATE proc test1
as 

declare @t1 int ;
select @t1=1

;
return @t1
begin transaction

declare @current_step_id uniqueidentifier
declare @t_test_id uniqueidentifier 
declare @next_step_id uniqueidentifier
declare @seconds_remain int 

select @current_step_id=current_step_id
from t_testing t inner join
t_testing_test tt on
t.t_testing_id=tt.t_testing_id
and t.current_test_id = tt.t_test_id
where t.t_testing_id=@t_testing_id
commit transaction
SET XACT_ABORT OFF;

begin
 
 set @t_test_id = (select current_test_id from t_testing  where t_testing_id=@t_testing_id )

select @timelimitmin=isnull(timelimitmin,0)
from t_test 
where t_test_id=@t_test_id

begin

--set @seconds_remain=200


select  
@start_time=min(isnull(ts.view_date,getdate()))
--ts.view_date,
,@STOP_TIME_SEC=min(isnull(tt.STOP_TIME_SEC,0))
from t_testing_step ts
inner join t_test_step s on ts.t_test_step_id=s.t_test_step_id
inner join t_testing_test tt on s.t_test_id=tt.t_test_id 
where s.t_test_id=@t_test_id
and ts.t_testing_id=@t_testing_id
and tt.t_testing_id=@t_testing_id
set @seconds_remain=datediff(second, getdate(), @start_time )- isnull(@STOP_TIME_SEC,0) + (60*@timelimitmin)

end 


 /* save result and change status to end  */
 update  
 t_testing_step 
 set RESULT_TXT=@result_txt,
 t_testing_step_status_id = 3,
 result_date=getdate() 
 where t_test_step_id=@current_step_id
    and t_testing_id = @t_testing_id

CREATE procedure get_next_step_id 
@current_step_id uniqueidentifier,
@next_step_id uniqueidentifier OUTPUT

as 

declare @t_test_id uniqueidentifier
declare @step_order int
declare @next_step_order int



select @t_test_id = t_test_id, @step_order=step_order
from t_test_step 
where t_test_step_id = @current_step_id

select @next_step_order=min(step_order)
from t_test_step
where t_test_id=@t_test_id and step_order>@step_order

begin
  select @next_step_id=t_test_step_id
  from t_test_step
  where t_test_id=@t_test_id and step_order=@next_step_order

end
else 
set @next_step_id = null
